<main>

	<header>
		<h1>{{ title }}</h1>
		<p>How much progress has Clive made on his second album?</p>
		<p class="js-only"><small><em>(Click the song titles for more detail...)</em></small></p>
	</header>

	{# <section class="notice">
		<h2>Update 14/11/2023</h2>
		<p>The mixing is nearly done, and the tracks should be going for mastering by the end of November.</p>
